        <sponsor name-id="S311">Ms. Klobuchar</sponsor> (for herself, <cosponsor name-id="S319">Mr. Begich</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="S282">Mr. Nelson</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SSBK00">Committee on Banking, Housing, and Urban Affairs</committee-name>
